Alison LaPlaca https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alison_LaPlaca 0 Alison LaPlaca (born December 16, 1959) is an American actress best known for the role of acid-tongued yuppie Linda Phillips in the Fox sitcoms Duet and its spin-off Open House, both of which aired in the late 1980s.
